resources.string: "Lokhu kusula ulwazi olusetshenziselwe ukuxhuma kule nethiwekhi, kufaka phakathi iphasiwedi eilondoloziwe"

"Lolu hlu lokukhetha alivumelekile. Faka uhlu oluhlukaniswe ngekhoma lwezizinda ezikhishiwe."

"Ummeleli we-HTTP usetshenziswa isiphequluli kodwa ngeke isetshenziswe ezinye izinhlelo zokusebenza"
"Faka uhlu oluhlukaniswe ngokhefana lezizinda ezikhishiwe noma shiya kungenalutho.\nIsibonelo: example.com,mycomp.test.com,localhost"
"Cindezela inkinobho yokumisa okuvikelekile kwe-Wi-Fi ku-router yakho.\nIngabizwa nge-\"WPS\" noma iqukethe isimbuli ngakwesokunxele."
"Ngemva kokufaka iphinikhodi, ukusetha kungathatha amaminithi angafika ku-2 ukuqeda"
"I-WPS isivele iyaqhubeka futhi ingathatha amaminithi angafika ku-2 ukuqeda"
"Esinye isikhathi se-WPS siyaqhubeka. Zama futhi kumaminithi ambalwa."
"Vumela izinhlelo zokusebenza ezicele imvume yakho ukusebenzisa ulwazi lendawo yakho"
"Vumela i-Google isize izinhlelo zokusebenza ukucacisa indawo. Lokhu kusho ukuthumela idatha yendawo engaziwa ku-Google, ngisho noma zingekho izinhlelo zokusebenza zisebenzayo."

"Vumela isevisi yendawo ye-Google ukuthi iqoqe ulwazi olungaqondene namuntu olumayelana nendawo. Enye idatha ingalondolozwa kudivayisi yakho. Ukuqoqa kungenzeka noma lungekho uhlelo lokusebenza olusebenzayo."
"Azikho izinhlelo zokusebenza ezicele indawo kamuva nje"

"I-Google isebenzisa lesi sici emikhiqizweni njenge-Google Now ne-Google Amamephu. Ukuvula ukubikwa kwendawo kuvumela noma yimuphi umkhiqizo we-Google esebenzisa lesi sici igcina futhi isebenzise idatha yakho yendawo yakamuva yedivayisi ngokuxhumana ne-Akhawunti yakho ye-Google."

"Uma umlando wedawo uvuliwe kule akhawunti, i-Google ingagcina idatha yakho yendawo yedivayisi ukuze usetshenziswe izinhlelo zakho zokusebenza.

Isibonelo, i-Google Amamephu ikunika izinkombhandlela, futhi i-Google Now ingakwazisa mayelana nethrafikhi yokuhamba.

Ungavala umlando wendawo noma kunini, kodwa ukwenza kanjalo akuyisusi. Ukuze ubuke futhi uphathe umlando wendawo yakho, vakashela ku-maps.google.com/locationhistory."

"Lokhu kuzosusa wonke umlando wendawo obekwe kusuka kule divayisi yale-akhawunti ye-Google. Awukwazi ukuhlehlisa lokhu kususwa. Ezinye izinhlelo zokusebenza, okufaka phakathi i-Google Now, kuzomisa ukusebenza."
"I-%1$s ingaqoqa wonke umbhalo owuthayiphayo, ngaphandle kwamaphasiwedi. Lokhu kufaka idatha yomuntu siqu efana nezinombolo zekhadi lesikweletu."
"Ukuze ubuyekeze lesi silungiselelo, idivayisi yakho idinga ukuqaliswa kabusha"
"Hlola izinhlelo zokusebenza ezifakiwe nge-ADB/ADT ngokuziphatha okuyingozi"
"Thuthukisa ukubuka ngokucacisa okuphezulu noma isilinganiso sefremu esikhulu. Lokhu kuthinta kuphela izibonisi ze-Ultra HD. Ukushintsha lesi silungiselelo kuzoqala kabusha idivayisi yakho."
"Uhlelo lokusebenza olususwe iphutha lulinda okususa iphutha ukuba kunamathisele ngaphambi kokusayinda"
"Ukubuka okukhanyayo phakathi kwamawindi uma kudwetshwe nge-GPU"
"Kusuka kokuhle kuya kokubi kakhulu: okuluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka, okuluhlaza okotshani, okubomvu okukhanyayo, okubomvu"

"Idivayisi yakho nedatha yomuntu siqu ivuleleke kakhulu ekuhlaselweni yizinhlelo zokusebenza ezisuka kumithombo engaziwa. Uyavuma ukuthi nguwe kuphela onesibopho sanoma yikuphi ukulimala kudivayisi yakho noma ukulahlekelwa yidatha okungasuka kusukela ekusebenziseni lezi zinhlelo zokusebenza."
